How to Change Jenkins Home  Directory 

- Check your jenkins home > Manage jenkins > System configure 
- create a new folder 
- copy the data from old folder to new folder 
- Create / Update env variable JENKINS_HOME 
- Restart the jenkins service again 



Simple language  --- 

- Go to the current Home directory of the Jenkins 
- copy all the files present in the Current Jenkins files 
- and paste all the files where you want to make new directory for Jenkins . 
